imdb.plot outline: The New Eat Bulaga. Indonesia (originally Eat Bulaga. Indonesia) was a variety and game show In Indonesia produced by Television and Production Exponents, Inc., and last aired by ANTV Network. It was based on the Philippines' longest-running noon-time variety show, Eat Bulaga!, which made it the first Philippine TV show to be franchised in another country.
